Tiny Forest Home by Sokol Mehmeti⁠
⁠
"Deep in the woods, there lives a tiny mouse in his tiny home. 😊⁠
⁠
Everything asset is sculpted in Maya with its Sculpting tools and Re-Topo tool. Texturing is done in Substance Painter and the snow in Substance Designer. Used a top projected shader with displacement to make the snow. So that its a dynamic snow placement no matter how the assets are rotated. This was super useful when modifying the scene composition."⁠
